{"bangumi":{"date":"2017-07-07","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/f7/bf/203526_q2P6P.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/f7/bf/203526_q2P6P.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/f7/bf/203526_q2P6P.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/f7/bf/203526_q2P6P.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/f7/bf/203526_q2P6P.jpg"},"summary":"       在每一个角落都被探索完毕的世界中，唯一残留的秘境——大洞穴“深渊”。不知道延续到何方，深不见底的巨大纵向洞穴，栖息着各种奇妙奇怪的生物们，沉眠着现在的人类无法制造的贵重遗物。“深渊”那充满了不可思议的姿态吸引了人们，并驱使人们展开冒险。如此，多次挑战大洞穴的冒险者们，陆续得到了“探窟家”的名号。\r\n       住在建造于深渊边缘的城镇“奥斯”的孤儿莉可，梦想着有朝一日成为母亲那样伟大的探窟家，并解开深渊的谜团。这样的某一天，莉可在探索深渊的途中，捡到了有着少年样貌的机器人…？","name":"メイドインアビス","name_cn":"来自深渊","tags":[{"name":"奇幻","count":3969,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":3115,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":2796,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017年7月","count":2318,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猎奇","count":2313,"total_cont":0},{"name":"来自深渊","count":2213,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":1962,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":1666,"total_cont":0},{"name":"KINEMACITRUS","count":1414,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017","count":1051,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":946,"total_cont":0},{"name":"致郁","count":822,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小岛正幸","count":573,"total_cont":0},{"name":"KINEMA_CITRUS","count":236,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":182,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小島正幸","count":111,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":62,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":55,"total_cont":0},{"name":"青年向","count":44,"total_cont":0},{"name":"催泪","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017年","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"KINEMA.CITRUS","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"异世界","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"倉田英之","count":24,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黄瀬和哉","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"仓田英之","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"正太","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"土笔章人","count":16,"total_cont":0}],